d customer service confirmation codes. And, of course, love letters.\n        \n \n        <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/notebook_std_01.jpg\" alt=\"Notebook Save The Date\" />\n\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/notebook_std_02.jpg\" alt=\"Notebook Save The Date\" />\n\n        Production Details\n        \n        <p>Client<br />\n        Self-Promotional</p>\n            \n        <p>Quantity Produced<br />\n        85</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Cost<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Time<br />\n        1 Month\n            \n        <p>Dimensions (Width &times; Height &times; Depth)<br />\n        4.1in &times; 5.8</p>\n        \n        <p>Page Count<br />\n        48 sheets</p>\n        \n        <p>Paper Stock<br />\n        Uncoated Craft</p>\n        \n        <p>Number of Colors<br />\n        1\n        \n        <p>Varnishes<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Binding<br />\n        Wire-Bound</p>\n        \n        <p>Typopgraphy<br />\n        Interstate<br />Magnel<br />Cheer Script</p>\n        \n        \n        \n \n        <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/images/advx3_rss_header.gif\" alt=\"Many thanks to our ADVx3 Partners\" />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/ck.php?oaparams=2__bannerid=17__zoneid=0__cb=b5cf3b2ed3__oadest=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neenahpaper.com%2Fclassic%3Futm_campaign%3DUnderConsideration_CLASSIC_OctNov2011%26utm_source%3DBanner\"><img src=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/avw.php?campaignid=3&amp;what=17&amp;cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE&amp;n=a8e15125\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/ck.php?oaparams=2__bannerid=19__zoneid=0__cb=34d6d77ea8__oadest=http%3A%2F%2Fbranding.sva.edu%2F\"><img src=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/avw.php?campaignid=4&amp;what=19&amp;cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE&amp;n=a08973cc\" /><