lation de contenus, les procÃƒÂ©dÃƒÂ©s dÃ¢â‚¬â„¢impression, les moyens ÃƒÂ©conomiques de fabrication et les notions de goÃƒÂ»t ou de fascination pour des sujets ou des images aussi diverses que spÃƒÂ©cifiques.</p>\n<p>12 mai &#8211; 21 juillet 2012, <a href=\"http://mediatheque.ville-nevers.fr\">MÃƒÂ©diathÃƒÂ¨que Jean JaurÃƒÂ¨s</a> &#38; <a href=\"http://galerie.arko.free.fr/dotclear/index.php?2012/05/04/48-impressed\">Galerie Arko</a>, Nevers<br />\n25 mai au 22 juin 2012, <a href=\"http://col58-billaut.ac-dijon.fr/welcome/index.php\">CollÃƒÂ¨ge Adam Billaut</a>, Nevers</p>\n',1,'2012-05-06 01:04:00','manystuff'),(223,4,'bf35b87fa8fa6b1faba094eff2f80473','http://www.creativeapplications.net/?p=24504','2012-05-10 09:35:15','Hartverdrahtet Ã¢â‚¬â€œ Infinite complexity in 4096 Bytes','http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/creativeapplicationsnet/~3/nbFwvNAf_pw/','','<p><a href=\"http://www.creativeapplications.net/windows/hartverdrahtet-infinite-complexity-in-4096-bytes/attachment/hartverdrahtet_1280x720_13/\"><img src=\"http://www.creativeapplications.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/hartverdrahtet_1280x720_13-640x360.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>Worthy winner of the PC 4kB intro competition at Revision 2012 and latest example of the compact-coding tradition exercised within the demoscene, <em>Hartverdrahtet</em> by Akronyme Analogiker is a three minute long audio-visual trip into a procedural fractalverse, compressed into a minuscule piece of software.<p><a href=\"http://www.creativeapplications.net/windows/hartverdrahtet-infinite-complexity-in-4096-bytes/?utm_source=feed&amp;utm_campaign=rss-mo-more&amp;utm_medium=rss\">Continue reading.... Hartverdrahtet Ã¢â‚¬â€œ Infinite complexity in 4096 Bytes</a></p>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?a=nbFwvNAf_pw:agaUF6zfuJ8:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?a=nbFwvNAf_pw:agaUF6zfuJ8:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?i=nbFwvNAf_pw:agaUF6zfuJ8:V_sGLiPBpWU\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?a=nbFwvNAf_pw:agaUF6zfuJ8:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?d=qj6IDK7rITs\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?a=nbFwvNAf_pw:agaUF6zfuJ8:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?i=nbFwvNAf_pw:agaUF6zfuJ8:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?a=nbFwvNAf_pw:agaUF6zfuJ8:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?i=nbFwvNAf_pw:agaUF6zfuJ8:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?a=nbFwvNAf_pw:agaUF6zfuJ8:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/creativeapplicationsnet?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\"></img></a>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/creativeapplicationsnet/~4/nbFwvNAf_pw\" />',1,'2012-05-10 09:18:21','Alexander Scholz'),(224,4,'633a8bb44d10a51a836794a73a37b4e7','http://www.creativeapplications.net/?p=24682','2012-05-10 09:35:15','Lightplot Ã¢â‚¬â€œ Robotic 3D light painting system by Ben Cowell-Thomas','http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/creativeapplicationsnet/~3/AAIiF7AvCoE/','','<p><a href=\"http://www.creativeapplications.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Cube_mid.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.creativeapplications.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Cube_mid-640x426.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>Created by Ben Cowell-Thomas,Ã‚Â Lightplot is a robotic 3D light painting system. Animation is exported from 3DS Max, and imported into the Lightplot software which then drives a robotic arm to draw the models in the air. The software also controls a DSLR camera to take long exposure photographs of each frame of animation<p><a href=\"http://www.creativeapplications.net/scripts/lightplot-ro