4/mEOcFrHW1KI\" />',1,'2012-05-24 12:32:00','bryonygp'),(344,7,'4e9739e7a43d02de3ba5455374b6fc4b','tag:www.underconsideration.com,2012:/fpo//1.1064','2012-05-25 21:58:01','Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters','http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/ucllc/fpo/~3/wqb-3twlrMQ/seamless-creative-cheers-coasters.php','','\n        <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_00.jpg\" alt=\"Lead Image\" />\n        \n        \n        Designed by <a href=\"http://www.seamlesscreative.com\">Seamless Creative</a>\n        \n        Printed by <a href=\"http://www.mamas-sauce.com/\">Mama\'s Sauce</a>\n        \n        I\'m forever on the hunt for the perfect coaster. This particular iteration scores big points for luscious printing and tiny details. The dazzling patterns are like a grown-up Spirograph for your grown-up beverage; you\'ll know you\'ve had enough when they start spinning. \n        \n \n        <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_01.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_02.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_03.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_04.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_05.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_06.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_07.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_08.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_09.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_10.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/seamless_coasters_11.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Creative Cheers Coasters\" />\n\n        Production Details\n        \n        <p>Client<br />\n        <a href=\"http://www.seamlesscreative.com\">Self-promotion</a></p>\n            \n        <p>Quantity Produced<br />\n        300</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Cost<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Time<br />\n        3 weeks\n            \n        <p>Dimensions (Width &times; Height &times; Depth)<br />\n        4 in &times; 4 in </p>\n        \n        <p>Page Count<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Paper Stock<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Number of Colors<br />\n        2\n        \n        <p>Varnishes<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Binding<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Typopgraphy<br />\n        Brandon Grotesque<br />FF Suhmo<br />Craw Modern<br />Filmotype Gay</p>\n        \n        <p>This piece is available for purchase for <a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/listing/91942184/cheers-screen-printed-coaster-set\">$14.00 plus $2.00 shipping</a></p>\n        \n \n        <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/images/advx3_rss_header.gif\" alt=\"Many thanks to our ADVx3 Partners\" />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/ck.php?oaparams=2__bannerid=17__zoneid=0__cb=b5cf3b2ed3__oadest=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neenahpaper.com%2Fclassic%3Futm_campaign%3DUnderConsideration_CLASSIC_OctNov2011%26utm_source%3DBanner\"><img src=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/avw.php?campaignid=3&amp;what=17&amp;cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBE