ogether the passion for wrapping with an actual product, well then, you just might be on to something like Carolyn Clingman managed to do.\n        \n \n        <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/paper_girl_wp_01.jpg\" alt=\"Papergirl Wrapping Products\" /> <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/images/divider_images.gif\" alt=\"---\" /><img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/paper_girl_wp_02.jpg\" alt=\"Papergirl Wrapping Products\" /> <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/images/divider_images.gif\" alt=\"---\" /><img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/paper_girl_wp_03.jpg\" alt=\"Papergirl Wrapping Products\" /> <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/images/divider_images.gif\" alt=\"---\" /><img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/paper_girl_wp_04.jpg\" alt=\"Papergirl Wrapping Products\" /> <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/images/divider_images.gif\" alt=\"---\" /><img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/paper_girl_wp_05.jpg\" alt=\"Papergirl Wrapping Products\" /> <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/images/divider_images.gif\" alt=\"---\" /><img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/paper_girl_wp_06.jpg\" alt=\"Papergirl Wrapping Products\" /> <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/images/divider_images.gif\" alt=\"---\" /><img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/paper_girl_wp_07.jpg\" alt=\"Papergirl Wrapping Products\" /> <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/images/divider_images.gif\" alt=\"---\" /><img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/paper_girl_wp_08.jpg\" alt=\"Papergirl Wrapping Products\" />\n\n        Production Details\n        \n        <p>Client<br />\n        <a href=\"http://papergirldesigns.net\">Papergirl Designs</a></p>\n            \n        <p>Quantity Produced<br />\n        Wrapping paper: 500 &times; 4 designs<br />Large cards: 250 &times; 6 designs<br />Small cards: 100 &times; 6 designs<br />Gift tags: 100 &times; 6 designs</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Cost<br />\n        Wrapping paper: $1,500<br />Cards: $1,200<br />Gift tags: $470</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Time<br />\n        Wrapping paper: 5 days<br />Cards: 4 days<br />Gift tags: 3 days\n            \n        <p>Dimensions (Width &times; Height &times; Depth)<br />\n        Wrapping paper: 18 in &amp;times 24 in<br />Large cards: 4.25 in &times; 6.25 in <br />Small cards: 2 in &times; 4 in<br />Gift tags: 2 in &times; 3.5 in</p>\n        \n        <p>Page Count<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Paper Stock<br />\n        Wrapping paper: 60# cougar opaque Smooth<br />Cards and Gift tags: 80# Finch Fine</p>\n        \n        <p>Number of Colors<br />\n        Wrapping paper, Cards, and Gift tags: CMYK\n        \n        <p>Varnishes<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Binding<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Typopgraphy<br />\n        Potato Cut</p>\n        \n        <p>This piece is available for purchase for  <a href=\"http://papergirldesigns.net\">$3 and up</a></p>\n        \n \n        <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/images/advx3_rss_header.gif\" alt=\"Many thanks to our ADVx3 Partners\" />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/ck.php?oaparams=2__bannerid=17__zoneid=0__cb=b5cf3b2ed3__oadest=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neenahpaper.com%2Fclassic%3Futm_campaign%3DUnderConsideration_CLASSIC_OctNov2011%26utm_source%3DBanner\"><img src=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/avw.php?campaignid=3&amp;what=17&amp;cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE&amp;n=a8e15125\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/ck.php?oaparams=2__bannerid=19__zoneid=0__cb=34d6d77ea8__oadest=http%3A%2F%2Fbranding.sva.edu%2F\"><img src=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/de