ntal graphics of a newly renovated facility. Before you get choked up on all that nostalgia, remember there\'s no crying in baseball. \n        \n \n        <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/fenway_01.jpg\" alt=\"10/100 Fenway Park Commemorative Book\" />\n\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/fenway_02.jpg\" alt=\"10/100 Fenway Park Commemorative Book\" />\n\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/fenway_03.jpg\" alt=\"10/100 Fenway Park Commemorative Book\" />\n\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/fenway_04.jpg\" alt=\"10/100 Fenway Park Commemorative Book\" />\n\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/fenway_05.jpg\" alt=\"10/100 Fenway Park Commemorative Book\" />\n\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/fenway_06.jpg\" alt=\"10/100 Fenway Park Commemorative Book\" />\n\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/fenway_07.jpg\" alt=\"10/100 Fenway Park Commemorative Book\" />\n\n<img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpo/project_images/fenway_08.jpg\" alt=\"10/100 Fenway Park Commemorative Book\" />\n\n\n        Production Details\n        \n        <p>Client<br />\n        Self-Promotional</p>\n            \n        <p>Quantity Produced<br />\n        1,000</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Cost<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Time<br />\n        2-3 weeks\n            \n        <p>Dimensions (Width &times; Height &times; Depth)<br />\n        6.5 &times; 9.25 &times; .375 in.</p>\n        \n        <p>Page Count<br />\n        108</p>\n        \n        <p>Paper Stock<br />\n        New Page / Centura / Matte / 100</p>\n        \n        <p>Number of Colors<br />\n        6\n        \n        <p>Varnishes<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Binding<br />\n        Exposed Smyth</p>\n        \n        <p>Typopgraphy<br />\n        