ect_images/fpoawards_earlybord_ends.png\" alt=\"Lead Image\" />\n        \n        \n        Designed by \n        \n        Printed by \n        \n        A friendly reminder that the last day to take advantage of the early-bird pricing for the <a href=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/fpoawards/\">FPO Awards</a> is this Friday, May 18. Prices go up on Saturday. You may complete the entry forms and pay by Friday and ship your materials later but before the final June 22 deadline.\n        \n \n        Production Details\n        \n        <p>Client<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n            \n        <p>Quantity Produced<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Cost<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Production Time<br />\n        &ndash;\n            \n        <p>Dimensions (Width &times; Height &times; Depth)<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Page Count<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Paper Stock<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Number of Colors<br />\n        &ndash;\n        \n        <p>Varnishes<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Binding<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        <p>Typopgraphy<br />\n        &ndash;</p>\n        \n        \n        \n \n        <img src=\"http://www.underconsideration.com/images/advx3_rss_header.gif\" alt=\"Many thanks to our ADVx3 Partners\" />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/ck.php?oaparams=2__bannerid=17__zoneid=0__cb=b5cf3b2ed3__oadest=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neenahpaper.com%2Fclassic%3Futm_campaign%3DUnderConsideration_CLASSIC_OctNov2011%26utm_source%3DBanner\"><img src=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/avw.php?campaignid=3&amp;what=17&amp;cb=INSERT_RANDOM_NUMBER_HERE&amp;n=a8e15125\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"http://underconsideration.com/oa_x/www/delivery/ck.php?oaparams=2__bannerid=19__zoneid=0__cb=34d6d77ea8__oadest=http%3A%2F%2Fbranding.sva.edu%2F\"><img src=\"http://underconsiderat